                    <h3>Hawkwood &mdash; Parks &amp; Recreations</h3>
                    <p>Offering some of the most breathtaking views of the Rocky Mountains and the city skyline, the community in Hawkwood is named after its original landowners Joseph and John Hawkwood.</p>
                    <h4>Hawkwood Real estate enjoys a gently sloping geography which lends the community a dream-like appeal.</h4>
                    <p>With its scenic walking trails, immaculate greens and lovely fountains and ponds, Hawkwood provides a charming and peaceful neighborhood for joggers, children and dog walkers alike. Apart from this, the community offers a range of recreational activities including playgrounds, parks, fields, shopping plazas and such for the local residents to enjoy their spare time.</p>
